sections.body:
Install Project B and start building:

```bash
npm install @example/project-b
# or
yarn add @example/project-b
```

```jsx
import { Button, Card, ThemeProvider } from '@example/project-b';
import '@example/project-b/dist/styles.css';

function App() {
  return (
    <ThemeProvider>
      <Card>
        <Button variant="primary" size="large">
          Get Started
        </Button>
      </Card>
    </ThemeProvider>
  );
}
```

For custom theming, create your theme configuration and pass it to ThemeProvider.
